{"tid":1391517,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[警告] 組隊先可以出任","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:57:12.000Z","uid":174541,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f75e24584262944d16a8f9dad59b2e0330dab8","tid":1391517,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"發夢見好多人都係幾個幾個咁出黎，出到黎先搵野做黎幫下手，<span style=\"color: red;\">好多時都唔知做緊乜咁幫....</span>攞729銅鑼灣至灣仔嘅人鏈為例，望落好勁好團結，實際效率欠奉，為傳而傳。<span style=\"color: red;\">做每一件事一定要有目標 預期效果 同 計劃!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以黎，大部分人就係無依個思想!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗住當日去到幫手就可以。要扭轉依個困局，就一定要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">自發組30人小隊</span></span>!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因有二<br />\n1. 人多自然安心，有自己人睇住背脊不安感大減<br />\n2. 一人計短 二人計長。有組織有計劃執行各種任務，由物資到實行亦可周詳計劃。用買裝為例，每人買啲點都方便過一條友去曬咁多地方買<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住平日係俾我地儲氣諗計再準備! 尤其是黎緊Hit and Run嘅不合作任務無計劃跟本無可能!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">組隊大法</span><br />\n搵到梗係搵啲自己識嘅人組啦(老母係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。無咁自已友就下次出黎見到邊啲投契嘅，做野差唔多嘅，吹幾句水試探下，ok嘅就開個tg grp計劃下次個任點做。講真，現場撚有咁多鬼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後一句!<br />\n無論你係物資 前線 建築 哨兵 法師 平民，我地都係香港人 都要團結 但願有天能以真面目相見!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7bb099b19c6eac541159513c9a8861f47b75f3","tid":1391517,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"266230e37de78f5f06edc183f910e81472178647","tid":1391517,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"組隊啊"},{"pid":"c060ab65243237e08b753423e80205e06e0af4cb","tid":1391517,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"團結啊"},{"pid":"d62a83a0285c31880d73634d7d9b6cd7a55cb176","tid":1391517,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b13bfd1fe65c710db610df3ff3053d51ec7260","tid":1391517,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"}]}